snippet.title: What Naomi Osaka Just Revealed About Meghan Markle
snippet.description:
After sitting out Wimbledon and withdrawing from the French Open, tennis star Naomi Osaka will be playing in the Tokyo Olympics. While it would be natural to assume a major tennis star like Osaka would be playing, this comes as a bit of a surprise considering her recent spats with the press. After missing her first interview during the French Open, she was hit with a $150,000 fine, which led Osaka to pen an op-ed for Time Magazine regarding her decision. In that same piece, she also mentioned a certain former British royal. Here's what Naomi Osaka just revealed about Meghan Markle.
